AB:
We present two families of exactly solvable interaction round a face (IRF) models associated with representations of the Lie superalgebras gl(m
) and sl(m
). These IRF models are the generalizations of integrable spin chains with bosons and fermions. We also presents fusion models associated with higher representations of gl(m
) and sl(m
). We introduce restricted IRF models both for gl(m
) and sl(m
).
